{"tid":1914981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚梁義士有樣野好奇怪，有冇人發覺？","createTime":"2020-03-08T01:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T03:42:41.000Z","uid":196227,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a5aa5492208880edc3f6717f39383a3b670bbfe1","tid":1914981,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚7:00-8:00呢段時間<br />\n首先有架狗車泊咗係條小路，之後有架白車黎咗<br />\n而架白車泊咗係架狗車前面成個鐘<br />\n<br />\n架白車係冇響過聲、著燈咁黎，泊咗個幾鐘痴住架狗車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟係<br />\n- 有人報救援黎到？（冇見醫護出入）<br />\n- 班狗征用架車？（浪費醫療資源）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想講既係班狗人手多撚到，每半個鐘換一批人黎罰企，其餘就番上架車休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個白衫仲不停玩手機<br />\n<br />\n仲有隻狗叫食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，PK鄧幾撚時告你條靚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴晚發生咗好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢件小事唔知需唔需要留意。"},{"pid":"014085708547148f099fb563abf41e0457aca910","tid":1914981,"uid":196227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:27:46.000Z","msg":"如果班狗可以隨便征用白車<br />\n手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e17f1d6601943b3f9522f01d394268fc8bdd07c","tid":1914981,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"014085708547148f099fb563abf41e0457aca910","tid":1914981,"uid":196227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:27:46.000Z","msg":"如果班狗可以隨便征用白車<br />\n手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"都好耐啦"},{"pid":"c07b1441d245191c2056b78699cbdde2464c9f4a","tid":1914981,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:34:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a41be596f5b0e6533c88d5ae5048758a96589490","tid":1914981,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdcff5adf0cdbb1df703c41cc2bc4cc3af253419","tid